{{!--
  PROFILE SECTION
  Mirrored from the HERO SECTION partial.
  Custom fields (set in Ghost Admin › Design):
    @custom.profile_name        — top label
    @custom.profile_title       — main headline
    @custom.profile_description — supporting paragraph
    @custom.profile_bullet_1/2/3 — tag pills
    @custom.profile_image       — portrait / right-side image (falls back to site cover)
--}}

<section class="profile" id="about" data-section-id="profile" data-home-profile-width="{{@custom.home_profile_width}}" data-profile-background="{{@custom.home_profile_background}}">
      <div class="profile-bg">
    <div class="profile-container">

      {{!-- LEFT: text content --}}
      <div class="profile-content">

        {{!-- Top label 
        <p class="profile-intro" id="profile-intro" data-animate="letter">
          {{#if @custom.profile_name}}{{@custom.profile_name}}{{else}}I'm Prem{{/if}}
        </p>--}}

        {{!-- Main headline --}}
        <h2 class="profile-headline serif" id="profile-headline" data-animate="word">
          {{#if @custom.profile_title}}{{@custom.profile_title}}{{else}}The design role is shifting.{{/if}}
        </h2>
        {{!-- Supporting description (each paragraph animates like testimonial cards) --}}
        <div class="profile-description" id="profile-description">

          <p class="profile-paragraph" data-card-reveal="default" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
           AI has collapsed the distance between idea and working product. The walls between strategy, design and engineering are dissolving into one faster loop. What's left scarce is judgment.  <br /><br />That's the model I work in.
          </p>
        </div>


        {{!-- Six items grid: how I work, in practice --}}
        <div class="profile-items" id="profile-items">
          <div class="profile-item" data-card-reveal="slide-left" data-item-index="0">
            <h3 class="profile-item-header">Partner</h3>
            <p class="profile-item-description">With engineers, product and executives, in their language. Influence earned by work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-item" data-card-reveal="slide-left" data-item-index="1">
            <h3 class="profile-item-header">Lead</h3>
            <p class="profile-item-description">Hands-on at one end; mentoring, vision and design ops at the other.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-item" data-card-reveal="slide-left" data-item-index="2">
            <h3 class="profile-item-header">Build</h3>
            <p class="profile-item-description">Close to code. Agentic-ready products, systems and teams. Capability that compounds.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-item" data-card-reveal="slide-left" data-item-index="3">
            <h3 class="profile-item-header">Care</h3>
            <p class="profile-item-description">Judgment, empathy, craft, coherence. That part stays human.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-item" data-card-reveal="slide-left" data-item-index="4">
            <h3 class="profile-item-header">Remove</h3>
            <p class="profile-item-description">More than I add. Killing bolt-ons and scope creep before they ship.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-item" data-card-reveal="slide-left" data-item-index="5">
            <h3 class="profile-item-header">Deliver</h3>
            <p class="profile-item-description">Value from day one, across 0→1→growth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
       
      </div>{{!-- /.profile-content --}}



    </div>{{!-- /.profile-container --}}

    </div>{{!-- /.profile-container --}}

</section>{{!-- /.profile --}}


{{!-- Animation handled by unified scroll-scrub-anim.js via initProfile() --}}
